Healing					KEY:Healing ~ WitchHex				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MinorHex																																DESC:The witch can soothe the wounds of those she touches.																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.66	BENEFIT:The witch may heal with a touch, this acts as a cure light wounds spell, using the witch's caster level.|PREVARLT:WitchLVL,5	BENEFIT:The witch may heal with a touch, this acts as a cure moderate wounds spell, using the  witch's caster level.|PREVARGTEQ:WitchLVL,5
Misfortune					KEY:Misfortune ~ WitchHex			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MinorHex					DEFINE:WitchMisfortuneRounds|1																						DESC:The witch can cause a creature within 30 feet to suffer grave misfortune.																																									BONUS:VAR|WitchMisfortuneRounds|1|PREVARGTEQ:WitchLVL,8	BONUS:VAR|WitchMisfortuneRounds|1|PREVARGTEQ:WitchLVL,16	SOURCEPAGE:p.66	BENEFIT:For %1 rounds, anytime the creature makes an ability check, attack roll, saving throw, or skill check, it must roll twice and take the worse result. A Will save negates this hex.|WitchMisfortuneRounds
