Tongues					KEY:Tongues ~ WitchHex				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MinorHex																																DESC:The witch with this hex can understand any spoken language.																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.67	BENEFIT:A witch with this hex can understand any spoken language for %1 minutes per day (in 1-minute increments), as per comprehend languages.|WitchLVL|PREVARLT:WitchLVL,5	BENEFIT:A witch with this hex can speak any language for %1 minutes per day (in 1-minute increments), as per tongues.|WitchLVL|PREVARGTEQ:WitchLVL,5
