# Ability Name	Unique Key					Category of Ability		Type							Description																																																							Damage Reduction	Source Page
Aura of Cowardice	KEY:Aura of Cowardice ~ Antipaladin	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DESC:You radiate a palpably daunting aura that causes all enemies within 10 feet to take a -4 penalty on saving throws against fear effects. Creatures that are normally immune to fear lose that immunity while within 10 feet of you. This ability functions only while you remain conscious, not if you are unconscious or dead.						SOURCEPAGE:p.120
Aura of Despair	KEY:Aura of Despair ~ Antipaladin	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DESC:Enemies within 10 feet of you take a -2 penalty on all saving throws. This penalty does not stack with the penalty from aura of cowardice. This ability functions only while you remain conscious, not if you are unconscious or dead.																				SOURCEPAGE:p.121
Aura of Vengeance	KEY:Aura of Vengeance ~ Antipaladin	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DESC:You can expend two uses of your Smite Good ability to grant the ability to smite good to all allies within 10 feet, using your bonuses. Allies must use this Smite Good ability by the start of your next turn, and the bonuses last for 1 minute. Using this ability is a free action. Good creatures gain no benefit from this ability.				SOURCEPAGE:p.121
Aura of Sin		KEY:Aura of Sin ~ Antipaladin		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DESC:Your weapons are treated as evil-aligned for the purposes of overcoming damage reduction. Any attack made against an enemy within 10 feet of your is treated as evil-aligned for the purposes of overcoming damage reduction. This ability functions only while you remain conscious, not if you are unconscious or dead.						SOURCEPAGE:p.122
Aura of Depravity	KEY:Aura of Depravity ~ Antipaladin	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DESC:You gain DR 5/good. Each enemy within 10 feet takes a -4 penalty on saving throws against compulsion effects. This ability functions only while you remain conscious, not if you are unconscious or dead.																						DR:5/Good		SOURCEPAGE:p.122

